 </media>
</figure>
</para>

<para id="speak"><title>2.  CLICKERS:  TEACHERS AND STUDENTS SPEAK</title>What are clickers, and why would you want to think about using them? Hear students and faculty at the University of Colorado at Boulder talk about what they think about clickers, and how they can be used to promote student learning. 

