 </media>
</figure>
</para>

<para id="effective"><title>3.  HOW TO USE CLICKERS EFFECTIVELY</title>Want to know more about just how to use clickers to best help your students learn? This video shares the best practices in clicker use, including tips on writing questions and getting students to talk about them, the finer points of running a class discussion about a question, and how long to allow for this process. VIEW THE FULL LENGTH VIDEO (12 minutes) at http://STEMclickers.colorado.edu.  

